Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.86,0:00:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時候的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.11,0:00:22.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不做出抉擇就必死無疑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.99,0:00:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃姐姐 不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.95,0:00:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要一個人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要死 帶濱路一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.17,0:00:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,濱路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.76,0:00:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊介
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.63,0:00:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.18,0:00:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們明明剛剛好不容易成為了一家人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.10,0:00:56.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想活下去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.11,0:01:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 做出選擇吧

Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:13.22,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:13.22,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.22,0:01:16.62,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.22,0:01:16.62,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:21.09,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.62,0:01:21.09,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:27.40,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乾いた風に抱かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.00,0:01:27.40,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迎面吹著乾燥的風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:33.87,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生命への 真偽を覚え 刻む想い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:33.87,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}懂得了生命的真偽 銘刻於心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.87,0:01:37.28,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}ただ 傍に居たいと願い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.87,0:01:37.28,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是 祈願待在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:39.85,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人を愛し 人を憎み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:39.85,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}愛過 恨過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:43.35,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲しさは  優しさ生む
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:43.35,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲傷最後化作溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.35,0:01:48.32,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}例え光が 消えたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.35,0:01:48.32,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算陷入無盡黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.32,0:01:53.09,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日の希望を探すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.32,0:01:53.09,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仍會尋覓明日希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:57.40,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃えた血の呼吸 消え寄せれば
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.09,0:01:57.40,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃燒的血液 停止了呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:02:02.47,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果は奇跡に変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:02:02.47,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果之緣 最終轉化成奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:04.67,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:04.67,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.67,0:02:07.14,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.67,0:02:07.14,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:10.88,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}闇を搔き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:10.88,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}撥開黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:14.71,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}手を伸ばすよ どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:14.71,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}伸手向前 追尋你到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:16.98,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.71,0:02:16.98,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.98,0:02:20.62,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}いつか 変えるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.98,0:02:20.62,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總有一天 命運將會轉變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:25.29,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}涙の意味 無駄にはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.62,0:02:25.29,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要讓眼淚白流
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:29.93,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}螺旋のように 蠢く果てに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.29,0:02:29.93,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如螺旋一般交織騷動的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.93,0:02:32.93,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(0,400)}吠えて 交わる FATE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.93,0:02:32.93,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(0,400)}狂吠吧 交織的命運

Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近還真是熱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 這不是河主大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我難得來乘涼不要嚇我嘛
